Audrey Hepburn was an icon.

Rising to fame in the 1950s, she was one of the greatest actresses of her era. In 1953, Hepburn became the first actress to win an Academy Award, a Golden Globe Award, and a BAFTA Award for a single performance: her leading role in the romantic comedy Roman Holiday.

Even today, over half a century later, she remains one of just 15 people to earn an â€œEGOTâ€ by winning all four major entertainment awards: Emmy, Grammy, Oscar, and Tony. By the 1960s, she was averaging more than one new film per year and, by everyoneâ€™s estimation, she was on a trajectory to be a movie star for decades to come.

fields.title: The Ultimate Productivity Hack is Saying No
fields.text:
he ultimate productivity hack is saying no.

Not doing something will always be faster than doing it. This statement reminds me of the old computer programming saying, â€œRemember that there is no code faster than no code.â€

The same philosophy applies in other areas of life. For example, there is no meeting that goes faster than not having a meeting at all.

This is not to say you should never attend another meeting, but the truth is that we say yes to many things we donâ€™t actually want to do. There are many meetings held that donâ€™t need to be held. There is a lot of code written that could be deleted.
fields.highlighted_text: But if the benefits of saying no are so obvious, then why do we say yes so often?

fields.title: What is Web3
fields.text:
Web3 is a new decentralized Internet. Decentralized means it doesnâ€™t have one company or organization that controls it. Instead many computers control it. A technology called blockchains connects the computers.

Some people like Web3. They spend money to make special apps. They run on blockchains. Other people canâ€™t turn them off. People can control their information.

Other people donâ€™t like Web3. They say that it is only an idea. They say that people will still need servers at big companies. They say that no rules can create problems.
fields.highlighted_text: Also, blockchains need a lot of power. This can hurt nature.

fields.title: Warner Bros. and Paramount Global may merge
fields.text:
wo big companies Warner Brothers Discovery and Paramount Global may merge. When two companies merge, they join together to make one big company.

The CEOs talk about it in Manhattan. They talk about making a very big media company. They have lots of movies and TV shows. The bosses meet to decide. But we do not know who will be the boss of the new company. It may be hard. Some people may not like it. There are official rules. They can have an impact on the merger.

Both companies have good things. Warner Brothers has its studios.  Paramount has a streaming service called Paramount Plus. We have to wait and see if they can join.

fields.title: The future of a steak
fields.text:
Company Micro Harvest is helping with the growing need for more protein.

They use tiny living things in a closed space, called a Bioreactor. This is a quick way to make protein. Other ways usually take a long time. Micro Harvest finishes the process in just one day. The protein which they make has a good taste.
fields.highlighted_text: The protein can go into different foods, even for pets. Bakers wants to start small, like in a local store or restaurant, and then grow. There are some rules to follow, but the company hopes that it will be possible to make food for people, too.

fields.title: China gaming rules
fields.text:
China makes new rules for video games. These rules stop people from spending too much money.

Big game companies like Tencent and NetEase lose a lot of money because of these rules. The rules say that games cannot give gifts for logging in or spending money. Investors worry. The companies lose almost 80 billion dollars. Tencent is one of the big companies. They do not need to change a lot and they follow the rules.

The rules also say that games can only let players spend some amount of money. Some rules may help the game industry. It will be easier to approve new games.

fields.title: 2023 top Google searches
fields.text:
Every year, Google makes a list of top searches. It tells us what information people search on the internet the most.

In 2023, people around the world want to know about Hamas. They search for things like â€˜war in Israel and Gazaâ€™, â€˜what is Hamasâ€™, or  â€˜what is happening in Israelâ€™. Other top searches include incidents such as the Titan submersible accident and the Turkey-Syria. The list includes the most important events and people, like Damar Hamlinâ€™s NFL game injury, actor Matthew Perryâ€™s death, and popular figures like Jeremy Renner and Andrew Tate.

With movies, â€˜Barbieâ€™ and â€˜Oppenheimerâ€™ are among the most popular searches.

fields.title: Dinosaur coins
fields.text:
The Royal Mint and the Natural History Museum make special coins with dinosaurs.

There are three coins with different dinosaurs â€“ tyrannosaurus, stegosaurus, and diplodocus. The coins have pictures by artist Robert Nicholls. Some are colorful. They show dinosaurs in places where they naturally live. Rebecca Morgan from the Royal Mint is happy about these new coins. Maxine Lister from the Natural History Museum likes that the coins have famous dinosaurs.

These coins are part of a series which celebrates old animals and dinosaurs. You can get them from the Royal Mintâ€™s website. The price starts at 11 pounds.
